<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('partials/head') %>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <div class="container-custom py-12 md:py-20">
            <header class="text-center mb-16">
                <h1 class="title font-cormorant text-5xl md:text-7xl text-accent-purple mb-4 font-medium">Success Stories</h1>
                <p class="subtitle font-cormorant text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gold leading-tight">Transformative Experiences from Our Community</p>
            </header>

            <section class="mb-20">
                <h2 class="font-cormorant text-3xl md:text-4xl text-accent-purple text-center mb-10 font-medium">Video Testimonials</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="relative pb-[56.25%] h-0 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border-2 border-accent-purple/10">
                        <iframe 
                            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full"
                            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sVPk0MXzuzM?si=vJKEXayc3p_hNMx1" 
                            title="YouTube video player" 
                            frameborder="0" 
                            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
                            referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" 
                            allowfullscreen>
                        </iframe>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative pb-[56.25%] h-0 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border-2 border-accent-purple/10">
                        <iframe 
                            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full"
                            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/TIyYyf2ruNY?si=vJKEXayc3p_hNMx1" 
                            title="YouTube video player" 
                            frameborder="0" 
                            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
                            referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" 
                            allowfullscreen>
                        </iframe>
                    </div>
                    <div class="relative pb-[56.25%] h-0 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border-2 border-accent-purple/10">
                        <iframe 
                            class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full"
                            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YfPAuGZRUnA?si=vJKEXayc3p_hNMx1" 
                            title="YouTube video player" 
                            frameborder="0" 
                            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" 
                            referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" 
                            allowfullscreen>
                        </iframe>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-20">
                <h2 class="font-cormorant text-3xl md:text-4xl text-accent-purple text-center mb-10 font-medium">Written Testimonials</h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12">
                    <div class="bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md text-center border border-accent-purple/5 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
                        <img src="/images/testimonial-avatar01.png" alt="Karen's avatar" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 border-4 border-accent-purple p-1">
                        <p class="text-dark-text italic text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">"The Ultra Breath technique changed my life completely. After just two weeks of practice, I noticed significant improvements in my sleep quality and overall stress levels. It's amazing how something so simple can be so powerful!"</p>
                        <p class="font-cormorant text-xl text-accent-purple font-medium">- Karen</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md text-center border border-accent-purple/5 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
                        <img src="/images/testimonial-avatar02.png" alt="Alex's avatar" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 border-4 border-accent-purple p-1">
                        <p class="text-dark-text italic text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">"I was skeptical at first, but the results speak for themselves. My anxiety levels have decreased dramatically, and I feel more centered and focused throughout the day. This program is truly transformative."</p>
                        <p class="font-cormorant text-xl text-accent-purple font-medium">- Alex</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-md text-center border border-accent-purple/5 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
                        <img src="/images/testimonial-avatar03.png" alt="Betsy's avatar" class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full mx-auto mb-6 border-4 border-accent-purple p-1">
                        <p class="text-dark-text italic text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">"The community support in Vagus Skool is incredible. Not only did I learn the techniques, but I also found a group of like-minded people who support each other's healing journey. It's been an amazing experience!"</p>
                        <p class="font-cormorant text-xl text-accent-purple font-medium">- Betsy</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <div class="text-center">
                <button id="cta-button" class="golden-button w-full md:w-auto mb-6">
                    Start Your Transformation Today
                </button>
                <p class="text-accent-purple text-sm md:text-base opacity-90">Join our growing community of transformed lives</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html> 